{"tid":908928,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【重獲臉龐】半塊臉被食肉菌侵蝕 勇媽：我當時就似科學怪人","createTime":"2018-11-20T03:19:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-21T02:22:27.000Z","uid":130626,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"f72b2eaffa29b618c3be4de15c0e120a2e11547e","tid":908928,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T03:19:54.000Z","msg":"英國一位媽媽去年跌傷後感染食肉菌，醫生及時處理救回她一命，不過手術後她半張臉慘被侵蝕，出院後連鏡子也不敢看，認為自己似「科學怪人」不想外出。她接受多次整容手術後，臉容修復情況良好，如今看來判若兩人，令人驚訝她這年來的變化竟然如此大。<br />\n47歲的科登（Donna Corden）去年初在廚房跌倒時，眉骨撞向焗爐被割傷，26歲女兒立即召救護車將她送院。不過科登病情急劇轉差，她的皮膚轉黑、腎臟出現衰竭及一度停止呼吸，醫生發現她感染了壞死性筋膜炎（necrotising fasciitis），如果再不處理，食肉菌恐會侵蝕她的腦部。<br />\n科登後來接受手術將臉上壞死細胞割走，令她失去半邊臉，之後陷入人工昏迷4天，再接受長達11小時手術，將部份大腿肉移植至臉上。科登醒來後形容自己似「怪物」，「我看似科學怪人，就似你在萬聖節時見到一個擁有巨大變形頭部的怪物。他們要移除我最大塊的大腿肉&hellip;&hellip;我一半臉沒有了，眼上也有一大塊要補，而這個欖球大小的肉就貼在我的臉上，我以為我無法再次外出」。<br />\n科登憶述：「我的睡房內有一面鏡&hellip;&hellip;但當我出院後我就將衣服掛在上面，不想見到自己，我也不再化妝，而且體重還增加了。」不過在醫生的巧手之下，她的臉容已經有了很大改變，令她重拾自信，她現在甚至能夠開玩笑說：「我日後可能會看來年輕20年呢。」<br />\n提起這次經歷，她很感激家人對她的支持，「這幾年過得很辛苦，但我有很好的家庭，根本不需要哭泣，我仍然生存就已經很幸運了&hellip;&hellip;我失去半邊臉了，當你重看照片後，你會發現自己改變了很多，壞死性筋膜炎非常罕見而且侵蝕速度很快，一小時就能破壞3厘米組織，有醫生發現到它我真的非常幸運」。<br />\n科登已經無法再透過國民保健署（NHS）援助做手術，日後要重塑容貌就要自費至少3萬鎊（30萬港元）醫療費用。她的朋友為她展開籌款活動，希望籌得所需的手術費。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181119/large/1542599648_3e93.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181119%2Flarge%2F1542599648_3e93.jpg&h=4e235159&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181119/large/1542599648_53cb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181119%2Flarge%2F1542599648_53cb.jpg&h=6c6c55a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181119/large/1542599648_a6a0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181119%2Flarge%2F1542599648_a6a0.jpg&h=7bd7ec7a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20181120/58930605\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181120%2F58930605&d=6bPelPYNlKPQ9BKRbB%2BhvQEk2Noh57F05xbgvjQdsX8%3D&h=30f58061\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181120%2F58930605&h=31ec4754\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20181120/58930605</a>"},{"pid":"a123ca003a4cf5785cb65576022c6a185ee217f8","tid":908928,"uid":76098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T03:25:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb5bcbf6c4b7e49405ef4dd08f0f6b34e071eba0","tid":908928,"uid":60057,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T04:14:15.000Z","msg":"連登從未令我失望，呢啲POST一定有圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10bfc969291d21d36c70ab9211aadf46e9aefab6","tid":908928,"uid":118623,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T04:17:08.000Z","msg":"成日覺得普通割傷都可以導致咁嚴重既後果好心寒"},{"pid":"5146b8512191a81e58592773e2dfb0f08da18661","tid":908928,"uid":48531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T04:26:25.000Z","msg":"點先可以避到食肉菌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59d7d9f0adf22db10bb51236eeeb7e15413a531e","tid":908928,"uid":130626,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"5146b8512191a81e58592773e2dfb0f08da18661","tid":908928,"uid":48531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T04:26:2